summary: Two rings which give 4000% magicka regen
descriptionHtml: Two magicka regen rings look at the screenshots to find them, the screenshot shows 1 but there is actually 2 rings. By the way these rings give you 4000% magicka regen OP I know but just made them for fun. You should NOT have problems with this mod, but problems could be caused by having an add-on that messes with the skyforge such as an Overhaul or not having a <!LEGIT!> copy of the game.
author: geno47
